Text: Smile Something new from AmazoncomIMAGE IMAGE Dear Amazon Customer Something exciting has developed at Amazoncom a new Camera Photo storeand right now you can get free prints Whether youre a novice or an ace Amazoncoms Camera Photo store is your fullservice resource for photography products services and information Youll find everything to fill your camera bagdigital and film cameras camcorders binoculars telescopes accessories and more Plus helpful reviews from our customers and expert editors buying guides and detailed product descriptions will help make purchasing the right products easy IMAGE IMAGE Get Free Prints IMAGE IMAGE IMAGE IMAGE IMAGE So stop in and check out the new Camera Photo Store And let us help you handle all of your photography needs Sincerely IMAGE Shawn Haynes Director Camera Photo PS We hope you enjoyed receiving this message However if youd rather not receive future emails of this sort from Amazoncom please visit your Amazoncom account page and under the Your Account Settings heading click the Update your communication preferences link Please note that this message was sent to the following email address
